{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-log-post-jsx","path":"/sass-opacity-percentage/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Percentage values are fine in css:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>but when used in sass, it will compile it to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>use floats instead:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sass\"><pre class=\"language-sass\"><code class=\"language-sass\"><span class=\"token property-line\"><span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.3;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Problems with opacity percentage in sass","date":"2021-03-17","tags":["sass","opacity"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/sass-opacity-percentage/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}